{"tid":309230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（你健康嗎？）哈佛科研男性每月射精21次減患癌風險22%","createTime":"2017-07-04T23:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T02:40:23.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c50d41d57c418bccca6ef561a3ae441006e87cf","tid":309230,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T23:51:50.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕年紀大的男人得攝護腺癌的機率高，最近幾年國外常有研究指出，只要男性多做愛或射精就可降低罹癌風險，不過衛福部桃園醫院泌尿科醫師莊恆彰認為，別為了降低罹患攝護腺癌的風險，就盲目追求射精次數，這不是正確的防癌方式！<br />\n美國哈佛大學過去曾有項研究調查指出，每月射精21次以上的男子，罹患護腺癌的風險會減少22%；加拿大蒙特利爾大學曾也發表一項研究調查，男性和超過20名女子做愛，可降低28%罹癌率。<br />\n《聯合報》報導，莊恆彰說，研究雖指多重性伴侶，能大幅降低攝護腺癌風險，但他認為此舉相當危險，很可能患性病、傳染病，過度的性愛行為可能會造成攝護腺發炎，長久下來也會癌變，他建議，別太在乎射精次數的多寡，健康的規律生活才是正確的保健方式。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2118468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2118468&d=aBFxeDEzZrt8zq9XuNrUMtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=372630a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2118468&h=cad23f81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2118468</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/074951_fde85d95d58569d2f083cc47f77ece86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F074951_fde85d95d58569d2f083cc47f77ece86.jpg&h=f9b82622&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/074955_f7103425a89a1487e7a86a635b2c53ef.jpg[/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F074955_f7103425a89a1487e7a86a635b2c53ef.jpg%5B%2F&d=aBFxeDEzZrt8zq9XuNrUMtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=60d2dd12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/074955_f7103425a89a1487e7a86a635b2c53ef.jpg[/</a><br />\n放心J吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a0ee82377561